name: Rosary Box
description: Decorated with Blessed Virgin Mary images and accented with gold painted trim, this round box is a perfect place to store one rosary or many! Included is a beautiful wooden rosary.

name: Skull Therapy Incense Kit
description: This beautiful skull shaped incense holder is decorated with loteria images and accented with two pink, artificial rose buds. On top of the skull has been drilled a tiny hole, perfect to hold any incense stick. This kit will include three incense sticks that promotes healing and comfort to the senses.

name: Tiger Lily
description:
Bold in both color and materials, this one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher is a must have! This piece is wrapped in white leather, decorated bright, red ribbon, salvaged silver jewelry, and a black arrowhead from a spiritual store in Southern California. 

It measures 5" wide x 17" long.

name: Dewy Day
description:
This charming little dreamcatcher is wrapped in white, RED HEART yarn and is adorned with various white ribbons. It is decorated with white feathers, peach artificial blossoms, and silver rhinestones. The webbing is made of waxed thread.

It measures 4" wide x 12" long.

name: Morning Dew
description: This one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher was inspired by the fresh morning dew in Springtime. This piece is adorned with RED HEART mustard colored yarn, white lace, artificial blossoms, and white feathers. The webbing is made of waxed thread and accented with rhinestones to resemble the delicacy of a morning's dew.

name: Skull Therapy
description:
This one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher is pretty adventurous. The juxtaposition between the lightness of the feathers and the bold turquoise skulls create a unique piece of art. It is adorned with RED HEART white yarn, turquoise skulls, white feathers and artificial cherry blossoms. The webbing is made of waxed thread. Each dreamcatcher is handmade and can never be reproduced. 

 

It measures 6" wide and 25" long.

name: Birds of A Feather
description: Light and airy, this one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher is the definition of precious. This dreamcatcher is decorated with RED HEART white yarn, an assortment of artificial blossoms, cream lace, large white feathers with black tips, and accented with pearl colored floral beads. The webbing is made of waxed thread and is adorned with two black feathers manipulated to resemble a heart.

name: Octopia
description:
This one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher is bold and enchanting. It's a journey to the bottom of the deep blue sea just waiting to be enjoyed. This dreamcatcher is adorned with RED HEART navy blue yarn, repurposed vintage jewelry, with cream, white and navy blue ribbons. The webbing is made of waxed thread with a salvaged piece of jewelry in the shape of an octopus and a thin glass vial with a special message inside. Each dreamcatcher is handmade and can never be reproduced.

It measures 7" wide and 14" long.

name: Gypsy
description:
This dreamcatcher is wrapped in white, RED HEART yarn, and white feathers. It is draped with various lace ribbons, gold and cream colored trimming and white feathers. The webbing is made of waxed thread, off white ribbon and the gold trimming.

It measure 9" wide x 25" long.

name: ROARING 20's
description:
White as a winter's snow, this one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher echoes the era of the Roaring 20's, where luxury and opulence were the norm. This unique dreamcatcher is simply covered with stark white feathers, pearl beads, and rhinestones. The webbing is made of waxed thread.

It measures 9" wide x 24" long.

name: Rose Garden
description:
This lovely, one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher is wrapped with white, RED HEART yarn and various white and gold ribbons. The webbing is made of waxed thread and decorated with a bountiful bunch of artificial gold-tipped, pink roses, a salvaged keychain heart from Japan, and topped with a delicate pink ribbon. 

It measures 10.5" wide x 32" long.

name: A Taste of Calle Lily
description:
This large, one-of-a-kind dreamcatcher is wrapped in white, RED HEART yarn, and is decorated with various white lace ribbons. The ring is adorned with white Calle Lilies. The webbing is made of waxed thread and is accented with two large black tipped feathers. 

It measures 13" wide x 27" long.
